tags.description: Cable Wharf in Northfleet, Kent, is a riverside housing development overlooking the Thames. Part of the Ebbsfleet Garden City project, it integrates modern homes with historical roots, referencing the site's legacy in telegraph cable production​.
tags.name: Cable Wharf
tags.note: Construction of Cable Wharf in Northfleet, Kent, began in 2019 as part of the Ebbsfleet Garden City initiative. The development will create 598 homes, with the project expected to be completed by 2035.
